How To Ruin Christmas actor Yonda Thomas has officially tied the knot to his long-time girlfriend Mumtaaz “Taz” Emeran. The couple got engaged when Yonda popped the big question in December 2021 after dating for six years. The couple’s wedding took place on April 3, according to Taz, who is also a fitness influencer. Taz took to her Instagram account to share their pictures looking ravishing in isiXhosa traditional attire.    Yonda and Taz join other celebrity couples who have also tied the knot this year including K Naomi, Denise Zimba, and Faith Nketsi. For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.